{"tid":2170095,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"生產過剩 華12萬個口罩製「迷宮」","createTime":"2020-08-23T04:35:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-23T05:00:10.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e45f4f9b0aa246157cc0601ea68b5d98e7a3aa68","tid":2170095,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T04:35:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200823/GV2OGX6HDNFZRLZ3ZM42IMFDPU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200823%2FGV2OGX6HDNFZRLZ3ZM42IMFDPU%2F&d=MZ%2BcikgbnzcLbT%2Fpq7%2BWTNnRRycoFBIefads3zMUO1U%3D&h=8a793b51\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200823%2FGV2OGX6HDNFZRLZ3ZM42IMFDPU%2F&h=cc3fa8bb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200823/GV2OGX6HDNFZRLZ3ZM42IMFDPU/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n生產過剩 華12萬個口罩製「迷宮」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/MTVMJMF4bJX0MPkaKdFG3S3escs=/1950x1024/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/RA7WQECYK5F7FGVPSCY7XPBSV4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FMTVMJMF4bJX0MPkaKdFG3S3escs%3D%2F1950x1024%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FRA7WQECYK5F7FGVPSCY7XPBSV4.jpg&h=c75ee3b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■有中國藝術家用12萬防塵口罩做藝術裝置。<br />\n<br />\n口罩在疫情爆發初期，可謂一罩難求。不過隨着疫情在中國趨緩、口罩大量生產，當局已逐漸放鬆管制，近日甚至有藝術團隊用近12萬個口罩製成「口罩迷宮」，反映中國為防疫過量生產口罩的情況。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n網民批評浪費<br />\n<br />\n來自中國、法國與英國設計師利用11.75萬個口罩，打造出兩個由口罩構成的獨特方形空間，於上月底舉行的蘇州第九屆「創博會（創意設計產業交易博覽會）」展出。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n聚合靈思團隊解釋，作品意念建基於「口罩」這一物品，已從純粹一塊纖維變成抗疫的符號，希望反映每個人抗疫的努力，。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n不過網民對這個創意做法並不收貨，反而批評是浪費。蘇州創博會解釋，。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n《江南時報》"},{"pid":"5c4e9d3e7e116bbadd12cff7beefdc11efc32e3f","tid":2170095,"uid":80164,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"